name: Nicole Lee
text: Wonderful staff and manager. I ran a fireworks tent in parking lot this summer. They made sure we ate great the whole 2weeks we were there. I highly recommend Marcos and the team at Fort Dodge!!

name: Todd Hall
text: Best place to order out in town. Never had a problem with orders or food. Customer service is great. Good people.

name: belinda cardona
text: Best sausage and green olive pizza in town. Friendly and clean place. Lots of coupons. Family place.

name: Josh Peart
text: Always phenomenal. We love the thin crust with all three crust toppers!

name: Summer Christensen
text: Ordered online food was delicious subs and pizza they were much faster than any other pizza places in town and the service was great.

name: Denver Snow
text: Great job friendly and caring service couldn't feel better about spending money

name: Ryan Andersen
text: The pizza is good but the service is horrible. Hopefully others receive better service then I did. Good luck.

name: quality fort dodge
text: love the staff and manager ..and the pizza is always cooked right and so so good..thanks Marcos Staff!!!

name: Craig Taylor
text: They have good pizza and wings as well as a good deal on movies with your purchase

name: Chad Barkley
text: Good pizza and good wings for a cheap price.

name: Don Wildt
text: Best  pizza,  subs and salad in town!

name: Patrick Roethler
text: Ate here several times, pizza is always hot and just GREAT toppings, I have had great luck with service--

name: Jason Neavin
text: Good pizza and real good bread sticks

name: Becky Antrim
text: Great pizza
